             was indicted for <rs id="t17820109-34-off183" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17820109-34-off183" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17820109-34-off183" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17820109-34-cd184" type="crimeDate">10th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17820109-34-off183 t17820109-34-cd184"></join> last, one watch, inside and outside cases made of silver, value 42 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17820109-34-victim463" type="victimName">
                           Sarah 
                           Davis
                        <interp inst="t17820109-34-victim463" type="surname" value="Davis"></interp>
